products.name: Refrigerator Defrost Thermostat
products.description: Defrost thermostat monitors temperature during defrost cycle. Prevents frost buildup.

products.name: Refrigerator Evaporator Fan Motor

products.name: Dishwasher Spray Arm - Upper

products.name: Dishwasher Drain Pump
products.description: Drains water from dishwasher after wash cycle. Replace if dishwasher won't drain or makes loud noise.

products.name: Dishwasher Water Inlet Valve
products.description: Controls water flow into dishwasher. Replace if dishwasher won't fill with water.

products.name: Dishwasher Door Latch Assembly
products.description: Door latch and handle assembly. Keeps door closed during operation.

products.name: Dishwasher Heating Element
products.description: Heats water during wash cycle and dries dishes. Replace if dishes aren't drying or water isn't hot enough.

products.name: Dishwasher Rack Roller
products.description: Lower rack roller wheel. Set of 8. Replace if rack doesn't roll smoothly.

products.name: Dishwasher Chopper Blade
products.description: Chopper blade for food disposal system. Grinds food particles during drain cycle.

products.name: Dishwasher Wash Impeller

products.name: Dishwasher Door Gasket
products.description: Door seal prevents water leaks. Replace if water leaks from door during operation.

products.name: Dishwasher Float Switch
